# roadMap_TMDB CLI APP

To go through the project requirement please click this: https://roadmap.sh/projects/tmdb-cli

To run this application, please make sure that you have an IDE or a terminal to run it.

Steps
    1. After you have cloned the app.
    2. cd to it, into 1. tmdb-cli app
    3. run npm install
    4. run npm link(Links you app globally so it can be run on any terminal or directory locally)
    5. When it is done you can any of the below command on your terminal terminal
        5.1 commands:
            tmdb-app --type playing
            tmdb-app --type popular
            tmdb-app --type top"
            tmdb-app --type upcoming